6 unit Turkey Sausage & Cheese Egg Bites
3 unit Sausage, Egg & Cheese Burrito
2 unit Banana Nut Muffin
2 unit Cinnamon Crumb Cake Muffin
2 unit Belgian Waffle
7 unit La Colombe Triple Lattes

EGG BITES:
MICROWAVE: Open plastic packaging slightly to vent. With egg bite in packaging, microwave until heated through, 40-60 seconds.
TOASTER OVEN: Preheat toaster oven to 350 degrees. Remove egg bite from plastic packaging and place in toaster oven. Cook until heated through, 5-10 minutes.

BURRITO:
RECOMMENDED: Unwrap burrito; loosely rewrap and place on a microwave-safe plate. Heat until warmed, rotating halfway through, 1½-2½ minutes. Let stand 1 minute. Unwrap and serve.
STOVETOP ALTERNATIVE (for crispy burritos): Follow microwave heating instructions. Remove burrito from microwave, carefully unwrap, and heat in a dry, preferably nonstick, medium pan over medium-low heat, about 45 seconds per side. (TIP: Use butter or oil if you like even crispier edges.)

MUFFIN:
Enjoy!

BELGIAN WAFFLE:
Heat a waffle iron. Add waffle to iron. Warm for about 30 seconds.
TOASTER OR OVEN: Heat toaster or traditional oven to low. Add waffle to toaster or oven. Warm for about 1 minute.
MICROWAVE: Microwave waffle for 20 seconds.

LATTE:
Serve over ice and enjoy!